<title>UK: Beale yr pretax profit rises 25 pct.</title>
<headline>Beale yr pretax profit rises 25 pct.</headline>
<dateline>LONDON 1997-01-31</dateline>
<text>
<p>Year to November 2, 1996.</p>
<p>				 (million stg unless stated)</p>
<p> Shr (pence)		25.8		   vs 20.7</p>
<p> Dividend (pence)	 5.75		   vs 4.50</p>
<p> Total dividend (pence) 8.3		    vs 6.7</p>
<p> Pretax		     4.0		    vs 3.2</p>
<p> Turnover		   55.6		   vs 46.3</p>
<p>NOTE - Full name of the British department store operator is Beale Group Plc. The figures exclude exceptional items.</p>
<p>--London Newsroom +44 171 542 4019</p>
